http://pandoc.org/demos.html


jch = example


HTML fragment:
pandoc jch.md -o jch.html


Standalone HTML file:
pandoc -s jch.md -o jch.html


HTML with smart quotes, table of contents, CSS, and custom footer:
pandoc -s -S --toc -c pandoc.css -A footer.html jch.md -o jch.html


Converting a web page to markdown:
pandoc -s -r html http://www.gnu.org/software/make/ -o jch.text


HTML slide shows:
pandoc -s --mathml -i -t dzslides jch.md -o jch.html
pandoc -s --webtex -i -t slidy jch.md -o jch.html
pandoc -s --mathjax -i -t revealjs jch.md -o jch.html